snippet.title: Raksasi Trailer (English) 2019.06.11
snippet.description:
Raksasi is a Top-Down perspective action game with random dungeons, heavy roguelike elements and intuitive soul-like fighting.
It's a challenging game. Be prepared to die and die some more times before you master it. :P
